data.description: Close to popular Gold Canyon Golf Resort! $10,000 New A/C! Furniture available on separate bill of sale! You'll love this immaculately designed 3 bed, 2 bath residence!This beauty offers a desert front yard, a 2 car garage, and an extended driveway. Be welcomed by the sizable living room adorned with vaulted ceilings, fresh paint, and wood style flooring. The eat in kitchen is a homemaker's delight, featuring built in appliances, lovely wood cabinetry, and sliding glass doors to the backyard. Main bedroom, perfect for a retreat a bay window, a full bathroom, and a walk-in closet. The well sized backyard has a covered patio and lots of space for memorable gatherings. It is conveniently located near restaurants, golf courses, and more. Hurry! This adorable single story is waiting for you!
